node.text:
This is for everyone who has smaller bags 💰 but wants to learn #nfts … I’m not sure if #worldofwomen will be a good investment or flip but I do know it’s a wonderful collection and a great discord community and I think y’all in here can learn a lot by going through the process of buying ETH and setting up a MetaMask and buying on OpenSea … might be fun to learn .. ❤️❤️❤️❤️🖼

Link to the project is in my profile ❤️❤️❤️🖼

Ps : clarification - female artist not full female team https://twitter.com/worldofwomennft/status/1417082405496754176?s=21

node.text: Work ethic matters .. 99% start with zero followers .. it takes work .. now,’ many can get burnt out because they are so impatient to get to “a million” followers that they look for every hack, cheat, quick ass move to get there, why? Because they need the clout or outside affirmation to feel better about the insecurity or because they think they’ll make $ and use it to buy things to impress people for outside validation. My friends .. the reason some don’t burn out even after putting in the work ethic is because they are patient and aren’t in need of “it” they love their craft, their art, their skill and ultimately “the process” aka “the game” .. that is where I am trying to get my community, because happiness is worth fighting for ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️

node.text: Something I am great at in content but not as much in day to day operations has been a huge change for me over the last 2 years, candor and especially kind candor has really changed my CEO life and I talk about my “1/2” in my new book @twelveandahalfbook

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Gary Vay-Ner-Chuk on September 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'TAKE A STEP BACK AND THINK ABOUT WHAT YOU LOVE DOING'.

node.text:
Y’all think this is some fantasy shit .. some nice to have .. some dream shit .. you think I’m ridiculous and don’t “get it”

And I think the reverse 🔄.. someone is right … and I got 10,000+ DM’s and emails from y’all telling me how shit changed when you got humble and accountable and started a new journey. 

I want y’all to win so bad .. ❤️❤️❤️… please realize you can be happy, in life, work, relationships, but it’s on you to stop being scared and take a step back for 1934 steps forward
